<h4>Buck requires Java 8</h4> 
<p>
Buck currently requires Java&nbsp;8; we are 
working toward support for future versions.  If you have multiple 
installations of Java on your development computer, 
you might get warnings from Buck that you are using an unsupported
version of Java. To resolve this issue, set 
the <code>JAVA_HOME</code> environment variable to the directory 
for <strong>version&nbsp;8</strong> of the Java Development Kit (JDK). 
Note that the directory that <code>JAVA_HOME</code> points to should 
contain a <code>bin</code> subdirectory which in turn contains binaries 
for the Java compiler (<code>javac</code>) and Java runtime (<code>java</code>).
</p>

